                            <comment id="95145" author="yong.fan" created="Sun, 28 Sep 2014 11:38:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It will be resolved in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5029&quot; title=&quot;LFSCK 5: The OST will use new FID sequence when detect inconsistent LAST_ID file&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5029&quot;&gt;LU-5029&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="88623" author="bzzz" created="Wed, 9 Jul 2014 17:53:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;iirc, there is another ticket (and a way) to improve this - do not block creations at all, just use a different sequence as all we need is unique FID.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
